Tapu Lele (TCG)

From Bulbapedia, the community-driven Pokémon encyclopedia.
Jump to navigationJump to search
← #0785: Tapu Koko
Pokémon
#0787: Tapu Bulu →
For Pokémon TCG Pocket cards, see Tapu Lele (TCG Pocket).

Tapu Lele has been featured on 6 different cards since it debuted in the Guardians Rising expansion of the Pokémon Trading Card Game. Tapu Lele cards are normally Psychic-type Basic Pokémon.

List of Pokémon cards featuring Tapu Lele

Tapu Lele
Cards listed with a blue background are only legal to use in the current Expanded format.
Cards listed with a green background are legal to use in both the current Standard and Expanded formats.
